  "merge_notes": "School conflict: ICT (2 sources) vs Price Action (1 source); picked ICT by majority. ICT definition emphasizes rapid V-shaped reversal and specific candle counts; Price Action definition is generic wedge/triangle. Identification rules combined; ICT rules are more operational. Common mistakes only from ICT.",
